<div id="settingsBg"></div>
<div id="settings" style="width:600px">
    <a href="javascript:void(0);" id="closeButton" style="float:right; display:block;">Close</a><br/>
    <br/>
    This is your game save data. Copy it and store at some safe place :)<br/>
    <textArea type="textArea" name="saveData" id="saveData" class="saveData"></textArea><br/>
    If you want to load a game, replace save game data and click
    <a href="javascript:void(0);" id="loadButton">LOAD</a><br/>
    <br/>
    <br/>
    {{#if hasPaypal}}
    This is your user hash. If you made any purchases, copy this to a safe place. All your purchases are bind to this
    hash. Keep it safe, as if it gets public purchases will be automatically disabled<br/>
    In case you switched computer or browser, copy old user hash here and update it. <br/>
    <input type="text" name="userHash" id="userHash" class="userHash"/><br/>
    <a href="javascript:void(0);" id="userHashButton">Update user hash (Will refresh the game!)</a><br/>
    <br/>
    <br/>
    {{/if}}

    <div style="text-align:center">
        <a href="javascript:void(0);" id="resetButton" style="color:red;">Hard reset</a>
    </div>
    <br/>
    <br/>
    <center>VER: 1.11</center>
</div>